A SELF PROCLAIMED DURBAN BASED MUSICIAN COULD SOON BE FACING THE MUSIC OF A DIFFERENT KIND AFTER HE POSTED A RACIST – HATRED POST TOWARDS WHITE MEN IN PARTICULAR. As a Black Man I can’t say I’m not thrilled about this, these pink people have to pay for what they did to my ancestors. I would love to open a museum of my collection of pink man skulls just for satisfaction and pride that I’ve Avenged my ancestors, and I know a lot of my black brothers feel the same way they just hiding it according to his facebook page he is the manager for Deo Volante Records they were approached for comment but no reply was received. 